thinking about his sister.  He ran outside, he would let out his anger.  He
didn't know if his anger and rage would help his high skill, or cut it down.
Oh well, he ran outside, and saw the three guys(R,D,G).  He grabbed out his
disc shooter and fired one at R, one at D and one at G(you know who I
mean,R-Rush D-Dark Lord and G-Grim Reaper).
